    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26a.16-17_0001"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">16</fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>Saturday</dateline>
                
                    <salute>Dear John,</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Robin Humphrey just wrote me about your wife. I am so very sorry. I know there is nothing anyone can say or do to make it easier but I did want you to know that my thoughts are with you and your family.</p>
                
                <p>Since I have known you I have felt very close to you and Mrs. Neihardt. When I was in Columbia it was like hav<del>e</del><add>i</add>ng a second family away from home. Again let me say that I am so very sorry.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Wity<sic>With</sic> deep affection,</salute>
                    
                    <signed>Sandy</signed>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
            
            
